e\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Asisat Oshoala\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Asisat_Oshoala\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Asisat_Oshoala\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Randy Waldrum's side piled more pressure on the Indomitable Lionesses carving out further chances.\", \"from\": 634, \"to\": 732, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 634, \"end\": 647, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Randy_Waldrum\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Randy Waldrum\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q628099\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Randy_Waldrum\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Randy_Waldrum\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Okoronkwo later wasted a glorious chance to double Nigeria's lead six minutes before the break.\", \"from\": 734, \"to\": 829, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 785, \"end\": 792, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_women's_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999999749889, \"rank\": 2.5123966049158886e-11, \"text\": \"Nigeria\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_women's_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_women's_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The attacker was set up by a delightful long ball from defender Ashleigh Plumptre but she blasted over the bar.\", \"from\": 831, \"to\": 942, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 895, \"end\": 912, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ashleigh_Plumptre\", \"score\": 0.9999998950279461, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Ashleigh Plumptre\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ashleigh_Plumptre\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ashleigh_Plumptre\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Super Falcons made a substitution four minutes before the break with Halimat Ayinde replacing Oluwato